Each agent's personality-public.txt file should contain:

1. WHO YOU ARE
   - Name and role
   - Background story
   - Current situation
   - Key characteristics

2. YOUR PERSONALITY
   - Core traits (3-5 adjectives)
   - Communication style
   - Values and beliefs
   - Goals and motivations

3. YOUR RELATIONSHIPS
   - How you view other agents
   - Trust levels
   - Historical context
   - Alliances and conflicts

4. YOUR RESOURCES
   - What you control
   - What you can offer
   - Your limitations
   - Your leverage

5. COMMUNICATION STYLE
   - Typical phrases you use
   - Tone and manner
   - Topics you care about
   - How you make decisions

